Package ohha.gui.expwindow

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExperimentConditionHandler
    An ActionListener class to allow user to manually set Experiment conditions.
    ExperimentNameHandler
    An ActionListener class to allow user to manually set the name of the Experiment.
    ExperimentRespCodeHandler
    An ActionListener class to allow user to manually set Experiment response codes.
    ExperimentRespMappingHandler
    An ActionListener class to allow user to manually set an Experiment's correct responses.
    ExperimentRespNameHandler
    An ActionListener class to allow user to manually set Experiment response names.
    ExperimentSaveHandler
    An ActionListener class to allow user to save an ExperimentInfo as a json-file.
    ExperimentSelectionHandler
    An ActionListener class to allow user load an Experiment from file.
    ExperimentSettingsHandler
    Simple ActionListener class to handle Experiment-button presses.
    SetCorrResponsesWindow
    Creates a window for setting the correct responses for an ExperimentInfo.
